---
title: Thai-Style Duck Curry with Basmati Rice
description: Ever-versatile duck breast ascends to a new level here in our Thai Duck Curry! This warming dish is filled with creamy coconut milk, flavourful Thai aromatics and spices, and a mouthwatering mix of fresh vegetables that will make it hard to put the spoon down!
